{"article_id":"VVg8AFf7iovPPYMs","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Trump edged closer to declaring a national emergency Thursday","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"that would allow him to build a barrier on the southern border","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"without Democrats ' approval ,","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"even suggesting","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"he might outsource some of the work to the state of Texas .","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"With no negotiations set","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"for resolving the 20-day-old partial government shutdown ,","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"Mr. Trump traveled to a Border Patrol station in McAllen , Texas ,","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"to meet with agents","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"and highlight the immigration and trafficking crisis .","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"He said","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"the collapse of talks with Democratic leaders a day earlier has nearly persuaded him of the need","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"to declare an emergency .","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"\" I have the absolute right","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"to declare a national emergency , \"","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"the president said .","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"\" If this doesn ' t work out ,","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"probably I will do it .","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"I would almost say","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"definitely .","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"I ' m prepared for anything . \"","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"At the Capitol , Vice President Mike Pence told reporters","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"that the president \" is going to get this done one way or the other . \"","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"\" There ' s no wall ,","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"there ' s no deal , \"","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"the vice president said .","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"An attempt by a small group of GOP senators","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"to strike an agreement","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"trading wall funding for full legalization of \" Dreamers \" here under the Obama-era DACA program","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"fell apart Thursday afternoon .","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"SEE ALSO :","depth":3},{"id":31,"text":"Trump may outsource border wall construction to Texas","depth":3},{"id":32,"text":"Democrats continued to push for an immediate reopening of the federal government ,","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"saying","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"they won ' t negotiate","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"until nine shuttered departments are back in business .","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"House Democrats passed two bills Thursday","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"to reopen some of those departments ,","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"but Senate Majority Leader Mitch McConnell blocked them in his chamber ,","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"saying","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"Mr. Trump would have vetoed them anyway .","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"House Speaker Nancy Pelosi accused Mr. Trump of creating a \" distraction \" from his \" other problems \"","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"- an apparent reference to special counsel Robert Mueller ' s investigation .","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"\" I don ' t even know","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"if the president wants the wall .","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"He wants a debate on the wall , \"","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"she said .","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"For his part , Mr. Trump flew about 1,700 miles Thursday to the Mexican border","depth":6},{"id":48,"text":"to show","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"that he wants a wall .","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"Following up on his address to the nation about a border crisis ,","depth":6},{"id":51,"text":"the president met with Border Patrol agents and other law-enforcement officials in Texas .","depth":6},{"id":52,"text":"During a roundtable discussion , Mr. Trump noted","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"that Texas Lt. Gov . Dan Patrick had suggested","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"providing the state with \" a relatively small amount of money ,","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"and they ' ll build a wall themselves . \"","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"\" I thought","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"that was not the worst idea","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"I ' ve ever heard , \"","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"he told Mr. Patrick .","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"\" Although I still think","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"I can do it cheaper than you .","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"I do like the idea .","depth":7},{"id":63,"text":"We ' re going to look at a couple of ways","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"of doing it ,","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"where you guys get [ the wall ] up .","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"I like that idea .","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"We ' ll take a look . \"","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"The president also heard from relatives of two law-enforcement officers","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"killed by illegal immigrants","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"- police Cpl . Ronil Singh of Newman , California , and Border Patrol Agent Javier Vega Jr. of Texas .","depth":7},{"id":71,"text":"Marie Vega recounted","depth":7},{"id":72,"text":"how her son was shot and killed during a robbery","depth":8},{"id":73,"text":"while on a family fishing outing in 2014 .","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"\" A parent should not have to bury their child , \"","depth":7},{"id":75,"text":"she told the president .","depth":7},{"id":76,"text":"\" We need the wall .","depth":7},{"id":77,"text":"We need tougher judges . \"","depth":7},{"id":78,"text":"Reggie Singh spoke of his brother ' s 5-month-old son","depth":7},{"id":79,"text":"having to grow up","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"without a father","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"after the corporal was shot and killed on the day after Christmas , allegedly by an illegal immigrant","depth":7},{"id":82,"text":"he pulled over in a traffic stop .","depth":7},{"id":83,"text":"\" What my family is going through right now , I do not want any other law-enforcement family to go through , \"","depth":6},{"id":84,"text":"Mr. Singh told the president .","depth":6},{"id":85,"text":"Others","depth":7},{"id":86,"text":"joining the president","depth":7},{"id":87,"text":"were Sens . John Cornyn and Ted Cruz , Texas Republicans ; Homeland Security Secretary Kirstjen Nielsen ; Customs and Border Protection Commissioner Kevin McAleenan ; and the head of the U.S. Army Corps of Engineers , Lt. Gen. Todd T. Semonite .","depth":6},{"id":88,"text":"The Army Corps would likely be in charge of wall building","depth":7},{"id":89,"text":"should Mr. Trump claim emergency powers ,","depth":7},{"id":90,"text":"and the White House directed them to examine supplemental funding","depth":7},{"id":91,"text":"to see what money could be used","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"if Mr. Trump declares a national emergency .","depth":8},{"id":93,"text":"And the president pushed back on critics","depth":7},{"id":94,"text":"who say","depth":8},{"id":95,"text":"he ' d be circumventing Congress ,","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"saying","depth":7},{"id":97,"text":"Capitol Hill approved the National Emergencies Act","depth":8},{"id":98,"text":"that would be the basis for his claims .","depth":8},{"id":99,"text":"He said","depth":7},{"id":100,"text":"declaring an emergency would be \" the easy route for me , \"","depth":7},{"id":101,"text":"and said","depth":8},{"id":102,"text":"he hasn ' t done it","depth":8},{"id":103,"text":"because he would still like to get a deal with Congress .","depth":7},{"id":104,"text":"The president blamed Democrats for the partial government shutdown ,","depth":7},{"id":105,"text":"rebutting their criticism","depth":8},{"id":106,"text":"that he has \" manufactured \" a crisis on the border","depth":9},{"id":107,"text":"to fulfill his 2016 campaign pledge","depth":10},{"id":108,"text":"to build a wall .","depth":10},{"id":109,"text":"Mr. Trump reiterated","depth":7},{"id":110,"text":"that their opposition is geared toward his re-election bid in 2020 .","depth":7},{"id":111,"text":"\" The Democrats don ' t care about crime .","depth":7},{"id":112,"text":"They ' ve been taken over by a group of young people","depth":9},{"id":113,"text":"who ,","depth":10},{"id":114,"text":"frankly , in some cases ,","depth":13},{"id":115,"text":"I ' ve been watching ,","depth":13},{"id":116,"text":"I actually think","depth":12},{"id":117,"text":"they ' re crazy .","depth":11},{"id":118,"text":"They have been taken over by a group of people","depth":10},{"id":119,"text":"that don ' t care about gangs ,","depth":11},{"id":120,"text":"they don ' t care about human trafficking and drugs ,","depth":12},{"id":121,"text":"they don ' t care about anything .","depth":12},{"id":122,"text":"I tell you what ,","depth":10},{"id":123,"text":"they have gone crazy , \"","depth":10},{"id":124,"text":"he said .","depth":6},{"id":125,"text":"The White House says","depth":9},{"id":126,"text":"it ' s made two different offers to Democrats , one in the early days of the shutdown and another after last weekend ' s work at Camp David .","depth":9},{"id":127,"text":"Mr. Pence said","depth":10},{"id":128,"text":"the first was rejected ,","depth":11},{"id":129,"text":"and there ' s been no movement on the second .","depth":11},{"id":130,"text":"That latest deal calls for combining $ 5.7 billion in border wall money with more immigration detention beds and more Border Patrol agents , reviving a program","depth":11},{"id":131,"text":"to allow children to apply for asylum from Central America ,","depth":11},{"id":132,"text":"and spending more money on medical care for migrants in U.S. custody and for screening traffic","depth":11},{"id":133,"text":"coming through official border crossings .","depth":11},{"id":134,"text":"\" It ' s hard for the American people to accept a party","depth":10},{"id":135,"text":"that won ' t even negotiate an agreement over border security","depth":10},{"id":136,"text":"is committed to border security , \"","depth":9},{"id":137,"text":"Mr. Pence said .","depth":8},{"id":138,"text":"Democrats say","depth":7},{"id":139,"text":"they ' re willing to talk ,","depth":9},{"id":140,"text":"but won ' t actually negotiate","depth":9},{"id":141,"text":"as long as part of the government is shut down .","depth":8},{"id":142,"text":"Mrs. Pelosi also said","depth":8},{"id":143,"text":"Wednesday ' s White House meeting ,","depth":10},{"id":144,"text":"where she refused any talk of wall money","depth":11},{"id":145,"text":"and Mr. Trump walked out ,","depth":11},{"id":146,"text":"was staged .","depth":9},{"id":147,"text":"\" I think","depth":9},{"id":148,"text":"it was a set-up","depth":10},{"id":149,"text":"so he could walk out , \"","depth":10},{"id":150,"text":"Mrs. Pelosi told reporters .","depth":8},{"id":151,"text":"Opponents say","depth":8},{"id":152,"text":"Mr. Trump ' s possible declaration of a national emergency would be met with an immediate court challenge","depth":9},{"id":153,"text":"to block his authority","depth":10},{"id":154,"text":"to build a wall unilaterally .","depth":10},{"id":155,"text":"He said","depth":8},{"id":156,"text":"the White House counsel ' s office has advised him","depth":9},{"id":157,"text":"that such a move is \" 100 percent \" legal .","depth":9}],"relations":[{"parent":315,"left":189,"right":314,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":189,"left":187,"right":188,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":187,"left":162,"right":186,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":162,"left":160,"right":161,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":160,"left":0,"right":159,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":159,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"mode","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":161,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":186,"left":177,"right":185,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":177,"left":166,"right":176,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":166,"left":163,"right":165,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"par